reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Perfect Addition to My Home - 5 Stars!
reviews.reviewText: I couldn’t be happier with my purchase of the rustic farmhouse coffee table! This charming piece has brought an enchanting touch to my living room, transforming it into a cozy haven.First and foremost, the craftsmanship is impeccable. The solid wood construction exudes durability and authenticity, making it a true standout in any rustic-inspired decor. The distressed finish adds character and tells a story of its own, bringing that sought-after vintage charm right into my home.The design is both functional and stylish. With its ample surface area, I can now comfortably entertain guests and display my favorite coffee table books and decorative pieces. The lower shelf is a thoughtful addition, providing extra storage space for magazines, remotes, or even a woven basket for added farmhouse flair.Assembly was a breeze, thanks to the clear instructions and all the necessary hardware provided. The table arrived in perfect condition, a testament to the careful packaging and handling by the seller.All in all, this rustic farmhouse coffee table has exceeded my expectations in every aspect. It’s not just a piece of furniture; it’s an investment that has truly elevated the aesthetics and functionality of my living space. I highly recommend it to anyone in search of a timeless and high-quality addition to their home. Five stars without a doubt!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Pros and Cons
reviews.reviewText: Pro: Overall the assembly was pretty straightforward. The table is attractive and serves its purpose.Cons: The screwdriver is "short" and can be difficult to use when attaching multiple screws. The bottom panels did not come with pre-drilled holes to secure the metal brackets. That was difficult if you didn't have a drill. Pre-drilled holes would have been appreciated.The two top panels on the table don't seem to flush. When assembled, one panel was about a 1/4 inch off from the other panel. I'm still trying to figure out why. The bottom panels are fine.The company apologized for the problem and offered a small refund. Great company to work with and very responsive to my emails.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Color. The table is nice.
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to do this review based on the Color. Depends on the lighting! I like it either way. The color here is grey wash. I would say the top of it is more brown. In the right light you can see a hint of grey in it. The sides are not white. It also has a hint of grey. ( lighting is key). It looks great either way. Wasn’t damaged in any way. Is sturdy. Quality is fine. For the price it is excellent. Mine is in a room that doesn’t get used and that is the reason I didn’t spend a fortune. I am pretty impressed and happy with the coffee table. It is exactly what I wanted.

reviews.reviewTitle: Für den Preis wirklich qualitativ gut
reviews.reviewText: Der Tisch sieht wirklich 100%-ig so aus wie auf dem Bild. Die Anleitung war wirklich einfach und unkompliziert. Alle Löcher waren vorgebohrt und alles hat ohne großen Kraftaufwand zusammen gepasst. Der Tisch ist optisch wirklich schön und wirkt auf mich hochwertig. Steht stabil und da wackelt wirklich gar nichts.Einzig eventuell die geteilte Tischplatte könnte ein Manko sein, weil sich in dieser Ritze gern Dreck ansammelt. Aber im Großen und Ganzen bin ich sehr zufrieden und würde den Tisch auch ein 2. Mal kaufen.
Material und die Verarbeitung sind top und der Aufbau ging Mega schnell.
